We're using APIs from the Dart plugin that don't exist in older version of the plugin; specifically, in the version of the Dart plugin that is compatible with Android Studio.

List of errors follow, but likely this will be addressed by https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/136; we should also work to reduce our exposure to dart plugin apis.
